"suppliers. To access it, go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Reporting --> "
"Partner Ledger`."
msgstr ""
"Il :guilabel:`Partitario clienti/fornitori` mostra il saldo di clienti e "
"fornitori. Per accedervi, segui il menu :menuselection:`Contabilità --> "
"Rendicontazione --> Partitario clienti/fornitori`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:194
#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/reporting.rst:103
