#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/get_started.rst:139
msgid ""
"You can also change the company's details by going "
"to :menuselection:`Settings --> General Settings`, scrolling down to "
"the :guilabel:`Companies` section, and :guilabel:`Update Info`."
