msgstr "Come l'imposta :ref:`appare ai clienti <taxes/configuration/customer>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:182
msgid "The details of the :doc:`tax computation <taxes/tax_computation>`"
msgstr "I dettagli del :doc:`calcolo dell'imposta <taxes/tax_computation>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:183
msgid "How tax payable journal items are :ref:`created <taxes/definition-tab>`"
msgstr ""
"Come vengono :ref:`create <taxes/definition-tab>` le voci contabili "
"dell'imposta da pagare"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/taxes.rst:184
msgid ""
":doc:`Fiscal positions <taxes/fiscal_positions>` (how to replace a tax by "
