msgstr "Quindi, convalida la :guilabel:`Liquidazione acquisti`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:604
msgid "Purchase withholding"
msgstr "Ritenuta d'acquisto"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:606
msgid ""
"*Purchase withholdings* are electronic documents sent to the SRI once "
"they're validated. They can only be registered from a validated (posted) "
"invoice."
msgstr ""
"Le *ritenute d'acquisto* sono documenti elettronici inviati all'SRI una "
"volta convalidati. Possono essere registrate solo da una fattura convalidata "
"(registrata)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:609
