msgstr ""
":ref:`localizations/hungary/taxes`: aliquote fiscali preconfigurate, incluse "
"IVA standard, supplemento compensativo, a tasso zero e opzioni esenti."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/hungary.rst:49
msgid ""
