msgstr ""
":ref:`localizations/hungary/tax-reporting`: panoramica dettagliata della "
"vostra responsabilità fiscale netta."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/hungary.rst:52
msgid ""
":ref:`e-Invoicing <localizations/hungary/e-invoicing>`: integration for "
"electronic invoicing using NAV 3.0 (Online Számlá) in line with the National "
