msgstr ":guilabel:`Report di localizzazione messicana Odoo`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:42
msgid "`l10n_mx_reports`"
msgstr "`l10n_mx_reports`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:43
msgid ""
"Adapts reports for Mexico's electronic accounting: chart of accounts, trial "
"balance, and |DIOT|."
msgstr ""
"Adatta i report per la contabilità elettronica del Messico: piano dei conti, "
"bilancio di verifica e |DIOT|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:45
msgid ":guilabel:`Mexico - Month 13 Trial Balance`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Messico - Bilancio di verifica del mese 13`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:46
msgid "`l10n_mx_reports_closing`"
msgstr "`l10n_mx_reports_closing`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:47
msgid ""
"Necessary to create the closing entry (also known as the *month 13 move*)."
msgstr ""
"Necessario per creare la registrazione di chiusura (nota anche come "
"*registrazione del mese 13*)."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:48
msgid ":guilabel:`Odoo Mexican XML Polizas Export`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Esportazione Polizas XML Messicano Odoo`"

