"Fai clic su :guilabel:`Aggiungi una riga`, seleziona i pagamenti che "
"desideri includere, fai clic su :guilabel:`Seleziona`, "
"quindi :guilabel:`Convalida`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_kingdom.rst:197
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/united_kingdom.rst:242
msgid ""
"Once validated, the Bacs file is available in the chatter. You can "
